{"title":"Chromatic dragon scales (EvilHack)","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Chromatic_dragon_scales_(EvilHack)","type":"markdown","data":"| \\[   chromatic dragon scales   |                                                                                                                               |\n| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Appearance                     | chromatic dragon scales                                                                                                       |\n|                                |                                                                                                                               |\n| Slot                           | [cloak](/wiki/Cloak \"Cloak\")                                                                                                  |\n| AC                             | [3](/wiki/Armor_class \"Armor class\")                                                                                          |\n| Special                        | - [magic resistance](/wiki/Magic_resistance \"Magic resistance\")\n- acts as a [light source](/wiki/Light_source \"Light source\") |\n|                                |                                                                                                                               |\n| Base price                     | 1500 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                                                                                            |\n| Weight                         | [40](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                                                                                                   |\n| Material                       | [dragon hide](/wiki/Dragon_hide \"Dragon hide\")                                                                                |\n\n**Chromatic dragon scales** are a type of [cloak](/wiki/Cloak \"Cloak\") that appear in [EvilHack](/wiki/EvilHack \"EvilHack\"). They are made of [dragon hide](/wiki/Dragon_hide \"Dragon hide\") like all [dragon scales](/wiki/Dragon_scales \"Dragon scales\").\n\n## Generation\n\nChromatic dragon scales are not randomly generated, though they can be found in [bones](/wiki/Bones \"Bones\"). [Wishing](/wiki/Wish \"Wish\") for a set of chromatic dragon scales will give the character a random set of normal dragon scales instead.\n\n[Tiamat](/wiki/Tiamat \"Tiamat\") has a 1⁄3 chance of leaving behind chromatic dragon scales upon death.\n\n## Description\n\nWhile worn, chromatic dragon scales confer 3 [AC](/wiki/AC \"AC\"), [magic resistance](/wiki/Magic_resistance \"Magic resistance\") and act as a [light source](/wiki/Light_source \"Light source\"). [Giant](/wiki/Giant_\\(starting_race\\) \"Giant (starting race)\") characters can wear chromatic dragon scales as one of the few cloak-slot pieces of armor that they are not too large for. When made into [dragon-scaled armor](/wiki/Dragon-scaled_armor#EvilHack \"Dragon-scaled armor\"), chromatic dragon scales confer a +5 bonus to AC along with several properties corresponding to specific colors of [dragon](/index.php?title=Dragon_\\(EvilHack\\)\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"Dragon (EvilHack) (page does not exist)\"):\n\n- [fire resistance](/wiki/Fire_resistance \"Fire resistance\")\n- [cold resistance](/wiki/Cold_resistance \"Cold resistance\")\n- [shock resistance](/wiki/Shock_resistance \"Shock resistance\")\n- [sleep resistance](/wiki/Sleep_resistance \"Sleep resistance\")\n- [poison resistance](/wiki/Poison_resistance \"Poison resistance\")\n- [disintegration resistance](/wiki/Disintegration_resistance \"Disintegration resistance\")\n- [acid resistance](/wiki/Acid_resistance \"Acid resistance\") and [stoning resistance](/wiki/Stoning_resistance \"Stoning resistance\") (yellow)\n- [reflection](/wiki/Reflection \"Reflection\") (silver)\n- [magic resistance](/wiki/Magic_resistance \"Magic resistance\") and [cancellation resistance](/index.php?title=Cancellation_resistance\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"Cancellation resistance (page does not exist)\") (gray)\n\n* *This page is a **[stub](/wiki/Category:Stubs \"Category:Stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Chromatic_dragon_scales_\\(EvilHack\\)\\&action=edit)*\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Chromatic dragon scales (EvilHack) - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Chromatic_dragon_scales_(EvilHack)\",\"wgTitle\":\"Chromatic dragon scales (EvilHack)\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":165604,\"wgRevisionId\":165604,\"wgArticleId\":40006,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Stubs\",\"EvilHack dragon armor\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Chromatic_dragon_scales_(EvilHack)\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":40006,\"wgRequestId\":\"cbb022a71fd3e42c36bcce77\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOptions\":\"{\\\"mode\\\":0,\\\"hideprefix\\\":20,\\\"showcount\\\":true,\\\"namespaces\\\":false}\"});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"user.options\":\"ready\",\"user.tokens\":\"loading\",\"mediawiki.legacy.shared\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.skinning.interface\":\"ready\",\"skins.vector.styles\":\"ready\"});mw.loader.implement(\"user.tokens@0tffind\",function($,jQuery,require,module){/*@nomin*/mw.user.tokens.set({\"editToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"patrolToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"watchToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"csrfToken\":\"+\\\\\"});\n});RLPAGEMODULES=[\"site\",\"mediawiki.page.startup\",\"mediawiki.user\",\"mediawiki.page.ready\",\"mediawiki.searchSuggest\",\"skins.vector.js\"];mw.loader.load(RLPAGEMODULES);});</script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmediawiki.skinning.interface%7Cskins.vector.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=startup&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector\"></script>\n<meta name=\"ResourceLoaderDynamicStyles\" content=\"\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=site.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"MediaWiki 1.32.5\"/>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Chromatic dragon scales are a type of cloak that appear in EvilHack. They are made of dragon hide like all dragon scales.\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Chromatic_dragon_scales_(EvilHack)\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Chromatic_dragon_scales_EvilHack rootpage-Chromatic_dragon_scales_EvilHack skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Chromatic dragon scales (EvilHack)</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-magenta\">[</span> &#8194; chromatic dragon scales &#8194;\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td>chromatic dragon scales\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Slot\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Cloak\" title=\"Cloak\">cloak</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>AC\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Armor_class\" title=\"Armor class\">3</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Special\n</th>\n<td><ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Magic_resistance\" title=\"Magic resistance\">magic resistance</a></li><li>acts as a <a href=\"/wiki/Light_source\" title=\"Light source\">light source</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>1500 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">40</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_hide\" title=\"Dragon hide\">dragon hide</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>Chromatic dragon scales</b> are a type of <a href=\"/wiki/Cloak\" title=\"Cloak\">cloak</a> that appear in <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>. They are made of <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_hide\" title=\"Dragon hide\">dragon hide</a> like all <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_scales\" title=\"Dragon scales\">dragon scales</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>Chromatic dragon scales are not randomly generated, though they can be found in <a href=\"/wiki/Bones\" title=\"Bones\">bones</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Wish\" title=\"Wish\">Wishing</a> for a set of chromatic dragon scales will give the character a random set of normal dragon scales instead.\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/Tiamat\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tiamat\">Tiamat</a> has a <sup>1</sup>&#8260;<sub>3</sub> chance of leaving behind chromatic dragon scales upon death.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>While worn, chromatic dragon scales confer 3 <a href=\"/wiki/AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"AC\">AC</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Magic_resistance\" title=\"Magic resistance\">magic resistance</a> and act as a <a href=\"/wiki/Light_source\" title=\"Light source\">light source</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Giant_(starting_race)\" title=\"Giant (starting race)\">Giant</a> characters can wear chromatic dragon scales as one of the few cloak-slot pieces of armor that they are not too large for. When made into <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon-scaled_armor#EvilHack\" title=\"Dragon-scaled armor\">dragon-scaled armor</a>, chromatic dragon scales confer a +5 bonus to AC along with several properties corresponding to specific colors of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragon_(EvilHack)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dragon (EvilHack) (page does not exist)\">dragon</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Fire_resistance\" title=\"Fire resistance\">fire resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Cold_resistance\" title=\"Cold resistance\">cold resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Shock_resistance\" title=\"Shock resistance\">shock resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sleep_resistance\" title=\"Sleep resistance\">sleep resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Poison_resistance\" title=\"Poison resistance\">poison resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Disintegration_resistance\" title=\"Disintegration resistance\">disintegration resistance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Acid_resistance\" title=\"Acid resistance\">acid resistance</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Stoning_resistance\" title=\"Stoning resistance\">stoning resistance</a> (yellow)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Reflection\" title=\"Reflection\">reflection</a> (silver)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Magic_resistance\" title=\"Magic resistance\">magic resistance</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Cancellation_resistance&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Cancellation resistance (page does not exist)\">cancellation resistance</a> (gray)</li></ul>\n<div class=\"stub\">\n<dl><dd><i>This page is a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">stub</a></b>. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Chromatic_dragon_scales_(EvilHack)&amp;action=edit\"><b>expanding this page</b>.</a></i></dd></dl>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182820\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 93/1000000\nPreprocessor